<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Crestline Auto Group — Marketing Strategy</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap');

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --navy:        #0d1b2a;
  --navy-mid:    #1a2e42;
  --navy-light:  #243d56;
  --navy-card:   #1e3448;
  --amber:       #c17f24;
  --amber-light: #e09b3d;
  --amber-dim:   rgba(193,127,36,0.15);
  --amber-border:rgba(193,127,36,0.3);
  --teal:        #004d50;
  --teal-accent: #00a8ae;
  --teal-dim:    rgba(0,168,174,0.12);
  --teal-border: rgba(0,168,174,0.3);
  --text-primary:#e8e0d4;
  --text-muted:  #8fa3b0;
  --text-dim:    #5a7080;
  --border:      rgba(193,127,36,0.18);
  --border-light:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  --font: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}

body {
  font-family: var(--font);
  background: var(--navy);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── HEADER ── */
.page-header {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 28px 40px 24px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.page-header::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -60px; right: -60px;
  width: 200px; height: 200px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(193,127,36,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.header-eyebrow {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--teal-accent);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.header-title {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.header-title span { color: var(--amber-light); }
.header-meta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 14px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.meta-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
.meta-dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--amber);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.meta-dot.teal { background: var(--teal-accent); }
.meta-dot.green { background: #4caf82; }
.header-score {
  position: absolute;
  top: 24px; right: 40px;
  text-align: right;
}
.score-num {
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--amber-light);
  line-height: 1;
}
.score-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.score-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber-light);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

/* ── TAB NAV ── */
.tab-nav {
  display: flex;
  background: var(--navy-mid);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 0 8px;
  gap: 2px;
  overflow-x: auto;
}
.tab-btn {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 140px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-family: var(--font);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 7px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.tab-btn:hover { color: var(--amber-light); background: var(--amber-dim); }
.tab-btn.active {
  color: var(--amber-light);
  border-bottom-color: var(--amber);
  background: var(--amber-dim);
}
.tab-icon { font-size: 14px; }

/* ── PANEL WRAPPER ── */
.tab-panel { display: none; padding: 32px 40px 48px; }
.tab-panel.active { display: block; }

/* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
.section-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.section-title-group {}
.section-eyebrow {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--teal-accent);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.section-subtitle {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* ── LAYOUT HELPERS ── */
.two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.three-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.full-width { margin-bottom: 24px; }

/* ── CARDS ── */
.card {
  background: var(--navy-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 20px;
}
.card-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.card-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--amber-light);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.card-body {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.card.teal-accent { border-color: var(--teal-border); }
.card.amber-accent { border-color: var(--amber-border); }
.card.highlight {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-mid) 0%, rgba(193,127,36,0.06) 100%);
  border-color: var(--amber-border);
}

/* ── STRATEGY CASCADE ── */
.cascade-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 16px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
}
.cascade-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.cascade-num {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--amber-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--amber-light);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.cascade-content {}
.cascade-q {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.cascade-a {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.cascade-a strong { color: var(--amber-light); font-weight: 600; }

/* ── TARGET CUSTOMER ── */
.persona-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.persona-card {
  background: var(--navy-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 18px;
}
.persona-name {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.persona-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--teal-accent);
  background: var(--teal-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--teal-border);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.persona-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  font-size: 12px;
}
.persona-row-label {
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-weight: 500;
  min-width: 80px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.persona-row-val { color: var(--text-muted); }

/* ── MESSAGING FRAMEWORK ── */
.message-block {
  background: var(--navy-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.message-header {
  background: var(--navy-mid);
  padding: 10px 18px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.message-channel {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber-light);
}
.message-type {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}
.message-body { padding: 14px 18px; }
.message-primary {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  font-style: italic;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.proof-points {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
}
.proof-pill {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  background: var(--navy-mid);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
}

/* ── CHANNEL TABLE ── */
.channel-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.channel-table th {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  text-align: left;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--navy-mid);
}
.channel-table td {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  padding: 12px 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  vertical-align: top;
}
.channel-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.channel-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
.channel-name {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.priority-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.priority-high {
  color: var(--amber-light);
  background: var(--amber-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
}
.priority-medium {
  color: var(--teal-accent);
  background: var(--teal-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--teal-border);
}
.priority-low {
  color: var(--text-dim);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
}

/* ── BUDGET BUCKETS ── */
.budget-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.budget-bucket {
  background: var(--navy-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 18px;
  text-align: center;
}
.budget-bucket.high { border-top: 3px solid var(--amber); }
.budget-bucket.medium { border-top: 3px solid var(--teal-accent); }
.budget-bucket.low { border-top: 3px solid var(--text-dim); }
.bucket-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.budget-bucket.high .bucket-label { color: var(--amber-light); }
.budget-bucket.medium .bucket-label { color: var(--teal-accent); }
.budget-bucket.low .bucket-label { color: var(--text-dim); }
.bucket-items {
  text-align: left;
  margin-top: 10px;
}
.bucket-item {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  padding: 4px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
}
.bucket-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.bucket-item::before {
  content: '';
  width: 4px; height: 4px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--text-dim);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ── MARTECH ── */
.martech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.martech-card {
  background: var(--navy-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 16px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
}
.martech-icon {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: var(--amber-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 16px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.martech-icon.teal {
  background: var(--teal-dim);
  border-color: var(--teal-border);
}
.martech-title {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.martech-desc {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.martech-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber-light);
  background: var(--amber-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
  padding: 1px 6px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.martech-tag.existing {
  color: var(--teal-accent);
  background: var(--teal-dim);
  border-color: var(--teal-border);
}

/* ── ROADMAP ── */
.phase-section { margin-bottom: 36px; }
.phase-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  background: var(--navy-mid);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
}
.phase-pill {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.phase-1 .phase-pill { color: var(--amber-light); background: var(--amber-dim); border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); }
.phase-2 .phase-pill { color: var(--teal-accent); background: var(--teal-dim); border: 1px solid var(--teal-border); }
.phase-name {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-primary);
}
.phase-timing {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-left: auto;
}
.phase-dep {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-style: italic;
}

.initiative {
  background: var(--navy-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
}
.initiative-num {
  width: 40px; height: 40px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.phase-1 .initiative-num { background: var(--amber-dim); border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); color: var(--amber-light); }
.phase-2 .initiative-num { background: var(--teal-dim); border: 1px solid var(--teal-border); color: var(--teal-accent); }
.initiative-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.initiative-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.initiative-meta {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
}
.meta-tag {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  background: var(--navy-mid);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
}
.meta-tag .tag-label { color: var(--text-muted); }

/* ── INSIGHT BOX ── */
.insight-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(193,127,36,0.08) 0%, rgba(0,77,80,0.08) 100%);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.insight-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber-light);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.insight-text {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

/* ── DEPENDENCY NOTE ── */
.dep-note {
  background: var(--teal-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--teal-border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.dep-note-icon { color: var(--teal-accent); font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

/* ── DIVIDER ── */
.divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
  margin: 28px 0;
}

/* ── SYNTHETIC NOTE ── */
.synthetic-note {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-style: italic;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 16px 40px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: var(--navy-mid);
}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .tab-panel { padding: 20px; }
  .page-header { padding: 20px; }
  .header-score { position: static; text-align: left; margin-top: 12px; }
  .two-col, .persona-grid, .martech-grid, .three-col, .budget-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .initiative { grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PAGE HEADER -->
<div class="page-header">
  <div class="header-eyebrow">Sample Work · Marketing Strategy</div>
  <div class="header-title"><span>Crestline Auto Group</span> — Marketing Strategy</div>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-dot"></div>Independent Used Car Dealer</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-dot"></div>Akron/Canton Metro · Ohio</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-dot teal"></div>14 Employees · $6.8M Revenue</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-dot green"></div>Synthetic Data — Illustrative Only</div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-score">
    <div class="score-num">52.2</div>
    <div class="score-label">SPDR Score</div>
    <div class="score-badge">Developing</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TAB NAV -->
<div class="tab-nav" role="tablist">
  <button class="tab-btn active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" id="tab-strategy" aria-controls="panel-strategy" onclick="switchTab('strategy')">
    <span class="tab-icon">◎</span> Marketing Strategy
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" id="tab-channels" aria-controls="panel-channels" onclick="switchTab('channels')">
    <span class="tab-icon">◈</span> Channels & Budget
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" id="tab-roadmap" aria-controls="panel-roadmap" onclick="switchTab('roadmap')">
    <span class="tab-icon">◇</span> Roadmap
  </button>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- TAB 1: MARKETING STRATEGY                -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="tab-panel active" id="panel-strategy" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-strategy">

  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-title-group">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Starting Point</div>
      <div class="section-title">Strategy Before Marketing</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">Marketing work follows business strategy — not the other way around</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="insight-box">
    <div class="insight-label">Key Insight</div>
    <div class="insight-text">Crestline had no documented marketing strategy because they had no documented business strategy. AutoTrader was the default lead channel — not a deliberate choice. Facebook Marketplace was active but informal. Reputation was building on its own, not by design. Before any marketing work could begin, the business strategy had to be written first. That's what made the rest of this possible.</div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRATEGY CASCADE -->
  <div class="card full-width">
    <div class="card-label">Business Strategy Cascade — Foundation for All Marketing Decisions</div>
    <div class="cascade-item">
      <div class="cascade-num">1</div>
      <div class="cascade-content">
        <div class="cascade-q">Winning Aspiration</div>
        <div class="cascade-a"><strong>Most trusted independent used car dealer for working families in the Akron/Canton metro</strong> — reputation that earns the first sale and brings customers back.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cascade-item">
      <div class="cascade-num">2</div>
      <div class="cascade-content">
        <div class="cascade-q">Where to Play</div>
        <div class="cascade-a">Akron/Canton metro and surrounding communities within a 60-minute drive. Target: <strong>working families and single-income buyers</strong>, $10K–$18K range, reliable daily driver, skeptical of dealerships — and willing to drive for a dealer they trust.</div>
